{"tid":108222,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[孝子陪雙親] 鬼國遊記之小明上廣州","createTime":"2017-02-05T05:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T12:12:26.000Z","uid":1301,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6740dec6387e35ba916b723477ee0481f1da38e2","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的 呢篇遊記係小弟上個星期<br />\n比老豆老母迫咗陪佢地上廣州玩3日2夜<br />\n<br />\nDay1<br />\n7 點半就比人踢咗落床出門口 <br />\n搭火車上深圳再搭搭高鐵上廣州<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/123503_4883abd94283c372d9a6524fb665def4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F123503_4883abd94283c372d9a6524fb665def4.jpg&h=3115f258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿途見到個呀伯攬住個孫仔坐係窗邊睇風景<br />\n很有愛的說～<br />\n<br />\n到咗廣州放低行李食個lunch <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3H4MD4n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3H4MD4n.jpg&h=4e994a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bE4aYk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbE4aYk2.jpg&h=42057f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(唔好睇佢樣衰衰 幾好味的）<br />\n就去咗香雪公園話睇梅花<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6c68F66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6c68F66.jpg&h=5103a0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到就真係乜柒花都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d 花已經開曬 所以呢到唔擺圖了<br />\n<br />\n去到夜晚 就去咗一間叫亨少嘅港式茶餐廳到食晚飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/124253_c15f3ed2f064e4ab066780efd4d51dde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F124253_c15f3ed2f064e4ab066780efd4d51dde.jpg&h=465e3ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢到d 野食幾好味 仲要超平！<br />\n呢碟德國鹹豬手先49人仔 <br />\n埋單3 個餸先120 蚊 抵到喊<br />\n食完去咗江邊影咗幾張夜景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/130055_9b89bb1cfc4007ca35265b4a1aeae1d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F130055_9b89bb1cfc4007ca35265b4a1aeae1d0.jpg&h=322b29ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02tM05q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02tM05q.jpg&h=cf72d0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後再去埋個m 記食個雪糕 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/595c9f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F595c9f2.jpg&h=c3eccd37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超多雪糕嘅麥旋風 仲要第二杯半價！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後基於小弟睡眠不足所以好早就返酒店訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ro60uO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ro60uO.jpg&h=818b2bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補多張酒店影嘅夜景先"},{"pid":"73a243762ca1a2657c3e0221fa0d584cc5f9f560","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ae9484214de9039eff90d722882a2f7c2d68e9","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"Day2<br />\n晨咁早比老媽子踢醒咗 攰撚死我呀真係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D10Uq8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD10Uq8O.jpg&h=b65be3d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過見到個天咁靚都精神返d<br />\n<br />\n第一站係去中山紀念堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FA24hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FA24hc.jpg&h=4e51eebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個建築風格幾靚 <br />\n但係唔撚明點解孫中山像下面要種花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地軍伐啦架屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway 跟住就去咗沙面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5T07wH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5T07wH.jpg&h=fb2cf427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙面其實係一個島仔<br />\n清朝個陣就係比洋鬼子攞黎通商嘅地方<br />\n所以建築風格係西式嘅<br />\n然後行過多少少就到咗個公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/130757_267381e7d8ff48c0138358e50fe6624e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F130757_267381e7d8ff48c0138358e50fe6624e.jpg&h=5b5f5b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有兩個呀伯係到彈結他 係幾好聽嘅<br />\n有點估唔到呢兩個呀伯可以合奏得咁正<br />\n(對唔住囉 我冇乜點影第二個呀伯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n然後就行下行下去咗步行街<br />\n見到有好多檔賣貓bb <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/131027_bfd764b17822f2f399648070427ff2c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F131027_bfd764b17822f2f399648070427ff2c3.jpg&h=48021350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超cute !! 但係係幾隻貓bb 困係貓籠入面慘叫<br />\n令人反思販賣動物嘅問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/131957_eaa0855876cde363cb89c6741db157f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F131957_eaa0855876cde363cb89c6741db157f7.jpg&h=7b6ed1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就搭地鐵去咗獵德大橋個邊影日落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/131311_9029d3c354c383a92610e3f1eb546263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F131311_9029d3c354c383a92610e3f1eb546263.jpg&h=4f0a5c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BB8e7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BB8e7R.jpg&h=e6bb0583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個日日落真心靚 配廣州例景日落<br />\n不過我得支雞腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋相機冇曬電 hea 影咗幾張就走了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超後悔做咩冇帶後備電出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而晚餐呢 就又係食返亨少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/131516_4a7577515def1415ffbde7df7ba38d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F131516_4a7577515def1415ffbde7df7ba38d72.jpg&h=84cddf24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超好味嘅魷魚 先好似30蚊左右 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p808O4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp808O4W.jpg&h=27a492ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫咗碟避風塘炒蟹 好似都係50 蚊左右<br />\n埋單叫咗4 個餸飽到嘔先得200 蚊唔到 <br />\n然後就回酒店訓覺了"},{"pid":"3c8f2d3b693b0cecb8fead3fdcfdafb5bab773c6","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"自己推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2283847fc9cf26bfe90778bc3d2ddda508b07b03","tid":108222,"uid":10224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"廣州人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15ffa53705adbfab25752d75395e25fd672e03c","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"Day3<br />\n一大早就去咗石室聖心大教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/132154_c9b3c7d782e1605da2f482a36481eb0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F132154_c9b3c7d782e1605da2f482a36481eb0e.jpg&h=258a2ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由法國佬係1863 年用咗哥德式風格起嘅教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3wpd1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3wpd1H.jpg&h=54426a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭巴士去教堂途中 個巴士司機突然用廣東話粗口狂鬧前面踩單車條友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :屌你老母識唔撚識踩單車呀臭閪 踩下又停下撞撚死你呀仆街<br />\n當堂覺得雖然講唔出咩大道理但係就覺得非常之有有親切感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n接着就馬不停蹄 (人不停腳？ 誤 ) 去咗黃埔古港<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/133040_f746f46209ddf9a6827ef4777b382059.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F133040_f746f46209ddf9a6827ef4777b382059.jpg&h=1ef5e9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇乜特別野睇 就當係到此一遊咁啦 <br />\n成個行程大概就完了<br />\n然後就當然高鐵火車咁坐到屎忽痛咁返屋企<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 1 我返到香港好似有點腹瀉嘅感覺<br />\n鬼國真係少去為妙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.s. 2如果大家鐘意小弟影嘅相 <br />\n可以follow 下小弟ig 大家交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  @Fujimountxssg  <br />\n<br />\nP.s.3 多謝大家睇我呢篇亂寫嘅文 <br />\n希望我仲有機會寫下呢d 文啦"},{"pid":"20ef9dff5d09ffe16e1046442a03d0e84366a7f0","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣州人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb98cb854361977f4bc179abf33aba538d0fcdf2","tid":108222,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"咩機？咩腳架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01550a9a246d8327a07b87ece3eb3ac27a457e2","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩機？咩腳架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFujifilm xe1 + 12 蚊店賣個隻腳架<br />\n有幾張係iphone 影嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639601c66aa1a05e34fb71a3f93900663edbe119","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842f33f7a2560e4b5cb9a888dbfc0cb09120c632","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"再推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a063cd109dcd82576c8330e66bbc100181e2112","tid":108222,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:01:54.000Z","msg":"上到廣州食呢D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139b0797ddf28b6785bd3cae1cbbf03b90af7915","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上到廣州食呢D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d 咩好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我完全冇做過research <br />\nBtw 我個陣年初4 上去咩鋪頭都冇開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2b504c57ae9ad74ebef93899b2ca9a584b3cab","tid":108222,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"上廣播仲食港式茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀記，南信，達揚，炳記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a83cc68c005d1868a12731bd82ef47d02e814af","tid":108222,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"沙面幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 10年前倒去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445446c192e2ec3438010387f4934f8926d5c438","tid":108222,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"廣州真係唔同鬼國同其他地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14c57e437b89959577f57136c173ad646d91f3a","tid":108222,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"我諗得廣州先唔會俾連登仔屌"},{"pid":"efb827378bbb8249b6bf7ae89d70b1b4da048315","tid":108222,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:05:20.000Z","msg":"新年上左廣州拜年<br />\n外省人北上曬條街真係好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976e536d293a3f92e7060bccd954d0c4fa18f299","tid":108222,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上廣播仲食港式茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀記，南信，達揚，炳記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀記啲腸粉好滑好好味"},{"pid":"8cc56693a5d21ef1ec66c4e644a37afc26b0ea3d","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上廣播仲食港式茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n銀記，南信，達揚，炳記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀記啲腸粉好滑好好味</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝推介<br />\n得閒陪多次老豆老母去食先"},{"pid":"4e7fb307e751a54e49f09b0abb1be5139d88ce4c","tid":108222,"uid":1301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:12:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕推一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}